keyFacts: JPMorgan Chase responded to an FBI subpoena on September 24, 2019 regarding case file SB106650241.
The bank's subpoena processing center is located in Fort Worth, Texas at 14800 Frye Road.
The FBI request was sent to their New York office at 26 Federal Plaza.
The document shows formal financial institution compliance with law enforcement investigative requests.
The case file number SB106650241 suggests this is part of an ongoing investigation.
